  devil-1.6.7-r1.ebuild:
  stable for x86

  25 Nov 2005; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org>
  +files/devil-1.6.7-sdl-checks.patch, devil-1.6.7-r1.ebuild:
  Fix by Henrik Dohlmann to make sure sdl libs/cflags arent used when sdl is
  disabled #113441.

  30 Sep 2005; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> devil-1.6.6-r2.ebuild,
  devil-1.6.7.ebuild, devil-1.6.7-r1.ebuild:
  Removed INSTALL.

*devil-1.6.7-r1 (30 Sep 2005)

  30 Sep 2005; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> devil-1.6.7.ebuild:
